'Lo Jordan, Go to the Server Download section. Pick a source and download it. Make sure that you have the lastest version of Java, because most of their Compiles & Runs will be formatted in the Jdk v6. If not, go and search for the Perfect Compiler - Made by Taharok.

Then go into the TuT section and read some Tuts. Try to find ones that’ll work on your server, unless you know how Java works and what to do. Some people are asses when it comes to Tuts, so you have to be a little more experience…
